user: I'm looking for some advice on data visualization tools. I'm a 32-year-old Asian American male working as a Senior Data Analyst, and I've been using Tableau for my projects, but I'm interested in exploring other options. Can you recommend some alternative tools that are popular in the finance and healthcare industries?
